<br>
Fortitude - not really needed with single target hero available at an earlier level. Doubt this spell will ever get upgraded. Yes it lasts a long time, but hero lasts pleanty long for those extra ac/hps.<br>
<br>
Mark of Karn - I agree that originally it was too powerful, but now it is a bit weak. A little tweak is all it needs.<br>
<br>
<br>
Ymaeel <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#313532><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/bbrellserilis.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=binge>Binge</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_bluespot.gif BORDER=0 HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>wang</span><br>  Posts: 1055<br> <font color=#CC9900>(4/17/01 9:56:27 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.wyattweb.com/users/monkeyo/monkey.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Should clerics spells be changed</span><hr size=1> Hammers, Yaulp fine, axe em, but umm they're not gonna, so dont get your hopes up.<br>
